{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"f1daf570-2a5f-47a7-b0cb-ffbe5a9fdc00","content":"Yes, you'll hit **framework compatibility issues**. Here's the breakdown:\n\n**Unsupported TFMs in MSTest v3:**\n- **`net5.0`** — EOL; MSTest v3 requires `net6.0` or later\n- **`netcoreapp3.1`** — EOL; also dropped in MSTest v3\n\n**Supported:**\n- **`net462`** — still supported ✅\n\n**Other migration notes:**\n1. **Package consolidation** — MSTest v3 uses a single `MSTest` package instead of separate `MSTest.TestFramework` and `MSTest.TestAdapter` references.\n2. You should update your TFMs to currently supported versions (e.g., `net6.0`, `net8.0`) before upgrading.\n\nA migrated `.csproj` would look roughly like:\n\n```xml\n<TargetFrameworks>net8.0;net462</TargetFrameworks>\n...\n<PackageReference Include=\"MSTest\" Version=\"3.x.x\" />\n```\n\nWould you like me to apply the migration?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"e85f5064-5be9-4efd-9e7c-399ae212f7df","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user's project targets:\n- `net5.0`\n- `net462`\n- `netcoreapp3.1`\n\nAnd uses MSTest v2.2.10 with separate `MSTest.TestFramework` and `MSTest.TestAdapter` packages.\n\nMSTest v3 has some important changes:\n1. **Package consolidation**: MSTest v3 uses a single `MSTest` meta-package instead of separate `MSTest.TestFramework` and `MSTest.TestAdapter`.\n2. **Dropped framework support**: MSTest v3 dropped support for older TFMs. Specifically:\n   - `net5.0` is no longer supported (it's out of support from Microsoft)\n   - `netcoreapp3.1` is no longer supported (also out of support)\n   - `net462` should still be supported (MSTest v3 supports .NET Framework 4.6.2+)\n\nSo the user will definitely run into compatibility issues with their target frameworks. They need to update their TFMs to supported ones like `net6.0` or `net8.0` (or later) for the .NET Core/5+ targets.","outputTokens":556,"requestId":"1BC2:315D54:A9BD65:C00249:6A03ED38"},"id":"34651a6b-0f86-484b-9824-947b019fc7c6","timestamp":"2026-05-13T03:17:24.515Z","parentId":"6d4967f5-7e01-4c3f-97a8-bdcd1455800c"}
